I mean even Kesha has worked in shelters for the homeless and spent alot of time working with people who&#8217;s lifes aren&#8217;t perfect. She was a poor child growing up and she takes the time to really work for her causes, Lady Gaga who lived this gifted life, went to one of the greatest colleges, and lived in New York ffs can&#8217;t spare a little money towards a cause she supports.<br />
It looks bad to me and it looked bad to me for a while.</p>
