<p>I love Lady Gaga, as you all should. She spreads love, acceptance, and bravery &#8211; a smart move that I say sells her music. Although, marketing technique or not, she was the one smart enough to do so. And while we &#8220;argue&#8221; about Lady Gaga, her music and motives, we should praise the advocacy work she has done to help the kids who are insecure. Haters hate.</p>
